<D>__{pig's ahead about a grand, shooter maybe three hundred.}
<P>__{(time lapse)}
<A>__{close shot cards being dealt sokal gets a nine of clubs, the kid a six, pig a queen, yeller a king, lancey a jack, and the shooter a four.}
<C>__{shooter's voice}
<D>__{king bets.}
<A>__{camera pulls back to show the players. there is less oral accompaniment to the betting now.}
