<C>__{bill}
<D>__{lancey could be laying for him with three jacks.}
<C>__{hoban}
<D>__{pig don't think so.}
<C>__{lancey's voice }
<D>__{call the two hundred.}
<B>__{the poker table}
<A>__{lancey puts in his money and so does sokal.}
<C>__{sokal}
<D>__{i'm sticking.}
<B>__{the poker table}
<A>__{shooter deals another round: an eight of clubs to sokal, a second seven to pig, a ten to lancey.}
